translation[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,Alif-Lâm-Mîm
  2,2,"Esi sisiBhalo ekungekho ntandabuzo kuso, sisiKhokelo kwabo bamoyikayo uAllâh"
  2,3,"Abakholwa kongabonwayo (uThixo), bamisele iSalâh1 bachithe2 (kumalizo) oko Sibaphe kona"
  2,4,Nabo bakholwa koko kutyhilwe kuwe3 nakoko kwatyhilwa ngaphambilikunaweyayebonabakholwangokunyanisekileyo kuBomi oBuzayo
  2,5,Aba ngabona bakwisiKhokelo (sokwenene) esivela eNkosini yabo yaye ngabo abaya kuphumelela